{"tid":1436271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］針對藍絲群組點應對？","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:32:52.000Z","uid":175033,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"26a1ac0138ab62ed79f48551749f8984df7b2d66","tid":1436271,"uid":175033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"點解佢哋成日Send啲完全荒謬嘅訊息都會有人信？<br />\n個人係因為仲未夠荒謬<br />\n每個人對荒謬嘅定義都唔同<br />\n因為唔同人嘅IQ都有高低之別<br />\n所以成堆冇腦藍絲先會信咁多呢啲資訊<br />\n<br />\n既然普遍大眾藍絲係唔會有獨立思想嘅<br />\n<strong>咁我地就send啲再荒謬嘅藍絲訊息出去<br />\n當佢哋懷疑訊息嘅可信性嘅時候<br />\n佢哋就會明白fact check嘅重要性<br />\n亦都會唸返究竟之前自己接收嘅資訊係咪正確</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd238f9e8ea8946c65126d211a5672594bf14b00","tid":1436271,"uid":175033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"367b574279734081a688dece1e6b8ad3e709085a","tid":1436271,"uid":175033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"1df83d4a55fbc91a906c9b8e73dad8a7d76c57e5","tid":1436271,"uid":175033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"0833c79afb916a89cdad2277df57f5bee5ef8ad6","tid":1436271,"uid":175033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"effaee5c5e5e5a7d7fd8c83d35116c27d11261a2","tid":1436271,"uid":223664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"但係我覺得愈post愈多 會令佢哋更加容易相信條信息（不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"02d276f27873ffeaee3611854e7c0613bed18422","tid":1436271,"uid":110683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"10000000放火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb60557fe301eff3ddd1dd2